<L>__{exterior palm grove night}
<A>__{chuck throws new firewood on the dwindling fire. it comes back to life. meteors streak again across the sky. he stares at the indifferent stars. the moon is almost full. shadows of palm trees sway on the sand.}
<L>__{exterior beach night}
<A>__{chuck stands by the edge of the water, which shimmers in the reflected light of the fire. a wave come in, licks at his toes. lifts up a coconut husk, sweeps it gently out. chuck watches, gets an idea.}
